{{Infobox airport | name = Paoua Airport | IATA = | ICAO = FEFP | type = Public | city-served = [[Paoua]], [[Central African Republic]] | location = | owner = Government | elevation-f = 2037 | elevation-m = | coordinates = {{coord|7|15|00|N|16|26|27|E|region:CF_type:airport|name=Paoua Airport (Paoua)|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Central African Republic | pushpin_label= FEFP | pushpin_map_caption = Location of Paoua Airport in the Central African Republic | metric-rwy = y | r1-number = 18/36 | r1-length-f = | r1-length-m = 1400 | r1-surface = Grass | footnotes = Source: Landings.com<ref name="Landings">[http://aerobaticsweb.org/cgi-bin/search_apt?FEFP Airport record for Paoua Airport] at Landings.com. Retrieved 2013-08-26</ref> Google Maps<ref name="Google">{{Google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?ht=en&z=13&t=k&q=7.25175,16.4407222222222+%28Paoua+Airport%29|title=location of Paoua Airport|accessdate=2013-08-26}}</ref> GCM<ref>{{GCM|FEFP|Paoua Airport}}</ref> }}
'''Paoua Airport''' {{Airport codes||FEFP}} is an airport serving [[Paoua]], a city in the [[Ouham-Pendé]] prefecture of the [[Central African Republic]]. The airport is on the northeast side of the city.
==See also== *{{portal-inline|Central African Republic}} *{{portal-inline|Aviation}} *[[Transport in the Central African Republic]] *[[List of airports in the Central African Republic]]
