{{Expand Italian|Diocesi di Kakamega|date=February 2011}} {{Infobox diocese |jurisdiction = Diocese |name = Kakamega |latin = Dioecesis Kakamegaensis |country = {{flag|Kenya}} |metropolitan = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Kisumu|Kisumu]] |rite = [[Latin Rite]] |cathedral = |cocathedral = |area_km2 = 3,517 |population = 1,988,123 |population_as_of = |catholics = 342,123 |catholics_percent= 17.2 |pope = {{Incumbent pope}} |bishop = [[Joseph Obanyi]] |coadjutor = |auxiliary_bishops= }}
The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Kakamega''' ({{lang-la|Kakamegaën(sis)}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Kakamega]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Kisumu|Kisumu]] in [[Kenya]].
==History== * February 27, 1978: Established as Diocese of Kakamega from the Diocese of Kisumu
