'''Sith FM''' is a temporary [[radio channel]] (96.1 MHz) which is done by the "Sith media circle" in "Sri Sudharmarama Purana Wihara", Muruththettuwa, Dehiowita, [[Sri Lanka]]. Its main ambition is to give experiences to the students in [[electronic media]] and how to perform their skills in front of a [[microphone]], in a radio channel.

